quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  36,55,"Toto abandu ba mumukunda kwomwikulu lelo bali khumilimo khubusangafu."
  36,56,"Bo nende abakhaye babu nibali mubinikha bayeshele khubisaala biobwokholo."
  36,57,"Balinyolamwo tsimbia tsioosi tsiebiamo, ne balinyoolamwo buli eshiabeenya."
  36,58,"“Omulembe” nilikhuwa lilirula khu Nyasaye Omulesi, Wobukoosia muno."
  36,59,"Ne enywe abetsimbii mwiyawule olwalelo."
  36,60,"Koo, shindalakana ninanyu enywe Abandu mbu mulalaama Shetani tawe? Toto ye ni Omusuku wenyu owa habulafu."
  36,61,"Ni mbu munaame esie. Ino niyo injila ingololofu."
  36,62,"Ne khubwatoto ye yakosia omukanda omukhongo mwinywe, koo shimwekhonyerangakhwo obwongo tawe?"
  36,63,"Mana ino niyo Jahanam yamwalakungwa."
  36,64,"Injilemwo lelo shingala mwakhayanga."
  36,65,"Olwa lelo khulatimbia eminwa chiabu, ne emikhono chiabu chilaboola ninafu, ne ebilenje biabu bilarusia obuloli khu kalia kabakholanga."
  36,66,"Ne khwenyanga, khwakhatimbiyie tsimoni tsiabu baba nibashilanila injila halali bakhalutsi barie?"
  36,67,"Ne khwenyanga, khwakhabakalukhaniye ifwani nibali hao butswa, mana shibakhanyalile okhutsia nohomba okhukalukha tawe."
  36,68,"Ne wakhukofusia, khumukalusinjia inyuma mubulonji, mana koo, shibeekhonyerangakhwo obwongo tawe?"
  36,69,"Ne shikhwamwechesia [Muhammad] amashairi tawe, ne elo shilienyekhana khuye tawe. Shino ni eshitsulisio nende Ikurani iretsanga abulafu."
  36,70,"Kho shikanyilisilie ushili omulamu, ne likhuwa libure khubakhayi."